{"tid":750012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾蔭權不適戴氧氣罩送瑪麗羈留病房","createTime":"2018-07-20T13:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T00:06:17.000Z","uid":11148,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"89b7332ba960f779a9d5be91ccea207337255ae1","tid":750012,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"前特首曾蔭權爵士去年2月在高院原訟庭被裁定一項公職人員行為失當罪成，判囚20個月。他就定罪及判刑提出上訴，上訴庭今(20日)駁回曾蔭權的定罪上訴，但刑期上訴得直，刑期減至12個月，訟費亦減至100萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n【19:13】至於早前兩次審訊均未達成大比數裁決的「行政長官接受利益」罪會否重審，律政司發言人指，會研究判案書和主控官的報告後再作決定，現階段不作評論。 <br />\n<br />\n【16:04】曾蔭權的代表律師余承章到羈留病房探望後離開，他指曾的身體「OK」，能夠交談，但拒回應曾是否氣促及不舒服，至於會否申請上訴及保釋，他則回應「唔識答」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180720/bkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180720%2Fbkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001.html&d=2Ff9JbElw05XPoJfiLQ2XviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a1218cfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180720/bkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180720/photo/bkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180720153050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180720%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180720153050&h=16788893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180720/photo/bkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180720194256\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180720%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180720101337217-0720_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180720194256&h=b4cdf4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691b8f4936ef31c4108bee6e17e425bc091a03f6","tid":75